text: Rafael José Orozco Maestre (March 24, 1954 – June 11, 1992) was a Colombian vallenato singer, songwriter and composer. Orozco Maestre died in Barranquilla at the age of 38, was killed by a shooter in front of his house. == References == Category:1954 births Category:1992 deaths Category:Assassinated people Category:Colombian singers
